| Column Name      | Data Type | Description        | Business Relevance            |
| ---------------- | --------- | ------------------ | ----------------------------- |
| CustomerID       | Integer   | Unique customer ID | Customer identification       |
| Name             | Text      | Customer name      | Customer tracking             |
| DOB              | Date      | Date of birth      | Age calculation               |
| City             | Text      | Customer city      | Location analysis             |
| Email            | Text      | Customer email     | Communication                 |
| RegistrationDate | Date      | Registration date  | Customer acquisition analysis |
| Customer_Age     | Integer   | Customer age       | Customer segmentation         |

